OL,3,CWoman dies and man arrested after
OL,4,CBelfast hit-and-run
OL,6,FA 24-year-old woman has died and a man
OL,7,Fhas been arrested following a hit-and-
OL,8,Frun crash in north Belfast.
OL,10,FRaven Adams, originally from the
OL,11,FTipperary area, died after she and a
OL,12,Fman were struck by a car.
OL,14,FThe man was also seriously injured in
OL,15,Fthe crash in the York Street Area at
OL,16,Faround 2.40am on Thursday.
OL,18,FThe driver of the car "fled the
OL,19,Fscene", police said, but was later
OL,20,Farrested.
OL,26,@zD@WOU{D@FO]
