OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1784315921
OL,3,CWoman dies and man arrested after
OL,4,CBelfast hit-and-run
OL,6,FDetective Inspector Stewart from the
OL,7,FPolice Service's collision
OL,8,Finvestigation unit said: "It was
OL,9,Freported the pedestrians were struck
OL,10,Fby a vehicle ` the driver of which, a
OL,11,F22-year-old man, subsequently fled the
OL,12,Fscene, and was later arrested by
OL,13,Fofficers in the nearby Cavehill area.
OL,15,F"He remains in police custody at this
OL,16,Ftime as enquiries continue into the
OL,17,Fcircumstances of what happened."
OL,26,@pD@ZOUwD@AOUyD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/6
