PN,41703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1784315921
OL,3,CWoman dies and man arrested after
OL,4,CBelfast hit-and-run
OL,6,FThe detective added: "Officers
OL,7,Fattended the scene, alongside
OL,8,Fcolleagues from other emergency
OL,9,Fservices where medical treatment was
OL,10,Fprovided to both pedestrians.
OL,12,F"Sadly, the female was pronounced
OL,13,Fdeceased at the scene, while the man
OL,14,Fhas been taken to hospital for
OL,15,Ftreatment of serious injuries.
OL,17,F"The road has now fully reopened
OL,18,Ffollowing a number of earlier closures
OL,19,Fin the area."
OL,26,@nD@VOUtD@AOUyD@AOU{D@MO]
