OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1784315921
OL,3,CWoman dies and man arrested after
OL,4,CBelfast hit-and-run
OL,6,FA local MLA said the community was
OL,7,Fleft "in shock" following the "very
OL,8,Fserious" road crash.
OL,10,FDUP MLA Philip Brett said he is
OL,11,F"deeply saddened" by what happened.
OL,13,F"The local community is in shock at
OL,14,Fthe seriousness of what has happened,
OL,15,Fand my thoughts are with everyone
OL,16,Faffected, together with their families
OL,17,Fand loved ones, at this incredibly
OL,18,Fdifficult time," he said.
OL,26,@oD@FOUoD@OO]oD@_OUpD@HO]sD@AOUsD@QO]uD@
OL,26,AAOUzD@PO]
