OL,3,CWoman dies and man arrested after
OL,4,CBelfast hit-and-run
OL,6,FHe added: "Finally, I want to pay
OL,7,Ftribute to the emergency services who
OL,8,Fresponded so quickly and
OL,9,Fprofessionally to what is clearly an
OL,10,Fextremely serious incident."
OL,12,FThe PSNI appealed to anyone with
OL,13,Finformation about the collision or who
OL,14,Fhas dash-cam footage of what happened
OL,15,Fto contact them using its witness
OL,16,Fappeal form at https:/
OL,17,F/reporting.psni.police.uk/appeals
OL,18,Fquoting reference 181 16/07/26 or
OL,19,Fcalling 101.
OL,26,@nD@KOUrD@\O]
